#. type: Title #
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Data-Binding"
msgstr "数据绑定"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "In Weex, we use the *mustache* syntax `{{...}}` to bind data in `<template>` which are defined in `<script>`. Once data and template is bound, the data changes will influence the corresponding template content immediately and automatically.\n"
msgstr "在 weex 中，我们使用 *mustache* 的语法 `{{...}}`，来绑定 `<template>` 模板 和 `<script>` 脚本 中的数据。 一旦 数据-模板 绑定了，脚本中数据的修改，会在模板的内容中实时生效。\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Binding data path"
msgstr "如何绑定数据？"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text style=\"font-size: {{size}}\">{{title}}</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      size: 48,\n"
"      title: 'Alibaba Weex Team'\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:25
msgid ""
"The code above will bind the `title` and `size` data field to `template`."
msgstr "上面的代码会把 `title` 和 `size` 绑定到模板上。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:27
msgid ""
"We can also use `.` syntax to bind cascading data structure. Let's look at "
"the following code snippet:"
msgstr ""
"我们也可以用 `.` 语法来绑定多层的数据结构。让我们来看看下面的代码片段："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text style=\"font-size: {{title.size}}\">{{title.value}}</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      title: {\n"
"        size: 48,\n"
"        value: 'Alibaba Weex Team'\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "In-template expression"
msgstr "模板表达式"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:50
msgid "Inside data bindings, Weex supports simply javascript expressions, e.g."
msgstr "在数据绑定中， weex 支持简单的 JavaScript 表达式计算，例如："

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"flex-direction: row;\">\n"
"    <text>{{firstName + ' ' + lastName}}</text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:67
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      firstName: 'John',\n"
"      lastName: 'Smith'\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:69
msgid "The expression will be evaluated in the data scope of current context."
msgstr "该表达式将在当前上下文内进行求值。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE: EACH BINDING CAN ONLY CONTAIN ONE SINGLE EXPRESSION**\n"
msgstr "*** 注意：每一个绑定只能包含一个表达式 **"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "Computed Properties"
msgstr "求值属性"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:75
msgid ""
"According to simple operations, in-template expressions are very convenient. "
"But if you want to put more logic into the template, you should use a "
"computed property."
msgstr ""
"简单的计算，用模板表达式非常方便。但是，如果你想把更多的逻辑放在模板中，你应"
"该使用一个求值属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"e.g.\n"
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"flex-direction: row;\">\n"
"    <text>{{fullName}}</text>\n"
"    <text onclick=\"changeName\"></text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      firstName: 'John',\n"
"      lastName: 'Smith'\n"
"    },\n"
"    computed: {\n"
"      fullName: {\n"
"        get: function() {\n"
"          return this.firstName + ' ' + this.lastName\n"
"        },\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        set: function(v) {\n"
"          var s = v.split(' ')\n"
"          this.firstName = s[0]\n"
"          this.lastName = s[1]\n"
"        }\n"
"      }\n"
"    },\n"
"    methods: {\n"
"      changeName: function() {\n"
"        this.fullName = 'Terry King'\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:114
msgid ""
"Here we have declared a computed property fullName. The function we provided "
"will be used as the getter function for concating firstName and lastName."
msgstr ""
"在这里，我们声明了一个求值属性 fullName 。 同时，定义了求值函数来连接 "
"firstName和 lastName 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:116
msgid ""
"Otherwise when you call `changeName` after click, the setter will be invoked "
"and this.firstName and this.lastName will be updated accordingly."
msgstr ""
"同时，当你点击调用 `changeName` 后， 会通过 set 函数来赋值，this.firstname "
"和 this.lastname 会相应的更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE: `data` and `methods` can't have duplicate fields. 'Cause in the execution context -- `this`, we can access both of them.**\n"
msgstr "**注意：`data`` 和 ``methods`` 的字段不能重复。 因为在执行上下文中 - 通过 `this`，我们可以同时访问这两者 **。 \n"

#. type: Title ##
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:119
#, no-wrap
msgid "Usage of some special attributes in Data-Binding"
msgstr "一些特殊属性在数据绑定中的应用"

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Styles: `style` or `class`"
msgstr "款式：`style`` or ``class`???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:124
msgid "the style of a component can be bind using the `style` attribute:"
msgstr "一个组件的风格可以用`style`属性绑定： ???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <text style=\"font-size: {{size}}; color: {{color}}; ...\">...</text>\n"
"</template>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:132
msgid ""
"while style can also get bound with `class` attribute, multiple classnames "
"can be split by spaces:"
msgstr "而风格也能得到一定`class`属性，多类名称可分空间： ???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container>\n"
"    <text class=\"{{size}}\"></text>\n"
"    <text class=\"title {{status}}\"></text>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:143
msgid ""
"here if `{{size}}` and `{{status}}` have empty value, then only `class="
"\"title\"` will be rendered."
msgstr ""
"在这里，如果`{{size}}`` and ``{{status}}`` have empty value, then only "
"``class=\"title\"`将呈现。 ???"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:145
msgid "[See more about style and class](./style-n-class.md)"
msgstr "[见更多的样式和类](./style-n-class.md)???"

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Event Handler: `on...`"
msgstr "事件处理程序：`on...`???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:149
msgid ""
"The event handler is an attribute which name has a prefix `on...`. The other "
"part of attribute name is event type and the value is event handler name. We "
"don't need to add mustache around the method name or add parentheses to call "
"it."
msgstr ""
"事件处理程序是一个属性的名称前缀`on...`。属性名称的另一部分是事件类型，值是事"
"件处理程序名。我们不需要添加胡子在方法名称或加括号来调用它。 ???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:154
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <text onclick=\"toggle\">Toggle</text>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:165
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    methods: {\n"
"      toggle: function () {\n"
"        // todo\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "`if` & `repeat`"
msgstr " `if`` & ``repeat`???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:169
msgid ""
"`if` attribute can control the display of a component by a truthy/falsy "
"value."
msgstr " `if`属性可以控制显示组件的一个真实性/ falsy价值。 ???"

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:177
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```html\n"
"<template>\n"
"  <container style=\"flex-direction: column;\">\n"
"    <text onclick=\"toggle\">Toggle</text>\n"
"    <image src=\"...\" if=\"{{shown}}\"></image>\n"
"  </container>\n"
"</template>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:191
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<script>\n"
"  module.exports = {\n"
"    data: {\n"
"      shown: true\n"
"    },\n"
"    methods: {\n"
"      toggle: function () {\n"
"        this.shown = !this.shown\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"</script>\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/dev/download/weex/doc/syntax/data-binding.md:193
msgid "We can also use `repeat` attribute to generate a list."
msgstr "我们也可以用`repeat`属性生成一个列表。 ???"

